Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.85,0:02:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得我爸内心是想被炒的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think my dad secretly wanted to get fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.40,0:02:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他总是把我妈离开这事怪在自己身上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Like, he always blames himself for my mom leaving
