Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.92,0:07:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 好的 拉吧 - 什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Okay, just pull. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.63,0:07:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想确定你觉得舒...没问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just want to make sure you're comf-- like, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.18,0:07:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 你就...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, yeah, just--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.02,0:08:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.27,0:08:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.07,0:08:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座城需要我们 如同我们需要它一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This town needs us. Just as much as we need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.82,0:08:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.82,0:08:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要敢想 就能随心所欲 混蛋们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, if you can see it, you can be it, motherfuckers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.96,0:08:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让2003年成为我们夺回 属于我们东西的一年\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, let 2003 be the year that we take back what's ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.92,0:08:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们颠覆这座城市吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's burn this city to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.76,0:08:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查尔斯 我脱不了上衣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Charles, I can't undo my top.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.27,0:08:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 是...叫我吗  - 你能...对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Is-- Is that me? - Can you-- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.48,0:08:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.90,0:08:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这里 对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right here. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.99,0:08:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.62,0:09:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 可以了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.17,0:09:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 谢谢 - 不用\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Thank you. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.72,0:09:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ten!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.97,0:09:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.97,0:09:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五 四\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Five! Four!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.39,0:09:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 查尔斯 你在哪里  - 我在这 你还好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Charles, where are you? - I'm here. Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.69,0:09:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.73,0:09:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新年快乐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.84,0:09:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过我会照顾你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I told you I would take care of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.43,0:10:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但似乎是你照顾我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but it looks like you're kind of the one taking care of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.39,0:10:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从没有这种经历\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Never really had that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.40,0:10:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.03,0:10:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你人真好 查理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're really nice, Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.63,0:10:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢...照顾你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I like-- I like taking care of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.77,0:10:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小萨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sam?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.68,0:10:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小萨 你说我可以告诉你任何事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sam, you said I could tell you anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.20,0:11:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得我得告诉你 我爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think I need to tell you that I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.58,0:11:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别干站着 我们得快点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't just stand there. We gotta hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.64,0:12:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一 二...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One, two and--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.65,0:12:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(中央公园警局)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.04,0:12:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(圣玛丽教堂)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.04,0:12:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(这是你一直在寻找的迹象)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.73,0:13:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴夫 是蕾根\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dave, it's Regan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.74,0:13:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听到这条留言后能不能立即回我电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you could call me back as soon as you get this message,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.83,0:13:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是关于我父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it's about my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.58,0:13:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比较急\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's time sensitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.87,0:13:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请录音 完成录音后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please record your message. When you have finished recording,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.54,0:13:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您可以结束通话或按“1”进行其他选择\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you may hang up or press one for more options.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.09,0:13:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾伦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alan,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.92,0:13:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的希望你没换号码 我想说 很抱歉打扰你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I really hope this is still your number and I would say, I'm sorry to bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.55,0:13:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我显然不是在打扰你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Except I'm clearly not bothering you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.47,0:13:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你像我们所谓法务团队的 其他九个成员一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}since you, like the nine other members of our legal so-called team,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.06,0:13:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不接电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}are not answering the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.06,0:13:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回我电话或让其他人打给我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Call me back or tell someone else to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.15,0:13:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要帮助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need help.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.15,0:14:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不...知道怎么...办\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't-- I don't know how to-- how to do this
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.86,0:14:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不知道这种情况该怎样或是否有用 但...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or how it works or if it works, but--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.82,0:14:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...知道我不能失去她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I-- I know I can't lose her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.22,0:14:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以...求求你 上帝 听到我的祈祷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So-- So, please, God, hear me pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.24,0:15:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通常会让大家单独待一会儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Like to give everyone a little alone time in here
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.28,0:15:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看会发生什么 一般有罪的人都会睡着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to see what happens. Guilty ones tend to fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.66,0:15:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不可能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No chance with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.50,0:15:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是无辜的 并且肾上腺飙升 极度焦虑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm innocent and wired on adrenaline and anxiety.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.50,0:15:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢嫌犯一上来就说自己是无辜的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Love it when a suspect tells me they're innocent right off the bat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.59,0:15:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉特别可信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It feels so believable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.42,0:15:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫌犯 我以为我是目击者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Suspect? I thought I was a witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.89,0:15:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古德曼先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, Mr. Goodman,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.47,0:15:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我们会发现你在现场 身上是血迹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}how'd it happen that we found you covered in blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.43,0:15:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兜里有毒品\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}bag of dope in your pocket,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.60,0:15:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站在一个头上有弹孔的女孩旁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}standing over a girl with a hole in her head?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.60,0:15:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你这么形容...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When you put it that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.81,0:15:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在开始前 我必须问...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Before we start, I have to ask--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.86,0:15:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 当然 你想要律师吗  - 不是问我的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Sure, do you want a lawyer? - Not about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.28,0:15:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩 她...会活下去吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The girl. She-- She going to live?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.12,0:15:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不确定 听上去不乐观\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not sure. Doesn't sound great.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.37,0:16:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你有宗教信仰 我本人是没有 我认为 是时候祷告了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you're a religious man, which I am not, I'd say now is the time to pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.75,0:16:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.73,0:16:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杨先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Yeung.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.11,0:16:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麦克法登警探 曼哈顿北区凶案组\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Detective McFadden, Manhattan North Homicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.65,0:16:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是负责你女儿一案的警探之一\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm one of the detectives working your daughter's case.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.82,0:16:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶杀  可是...她还活着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Homicide? But-- But she isn't dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.91,0:16:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.04,0:16:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你知道 如果发生了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But, you know, if anything changes,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.66,0:16:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只想确保没有漏掉任何细节\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we just want to make sure we didn't miss something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.25,0:16:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道 这种情况下派来的警探更优秀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, you get a much better class of detective this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.13,0:16:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信我 你不希望这起案件 由暴力犯罪组的那些小丑来负责\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And believe me, you don't want this handled by the jokers in violent crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.39,0:17:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道这是艰难的时刻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, I know this is a difficult time,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.35,0:17:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你介意我问你几个问题吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but do you mind if I ask you a few questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.02,0:17:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外套里有半克海洛因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Half a gram of heroin in that jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.28,0:17:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜你是买 不是卖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm assuming you were buying, not selling?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.32,0:17:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 两个都没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What? No, neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.03,0:17:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如我说的 那不是我的外套 我从不吸毒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Like I said, it wasn't my suit, and I've never done drugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.29,0:17:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Never?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.83,0:17:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 我吸过大麻 其实今晚吸过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay. Well, I have smoked pot. Tonight, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.17,0:17:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 等等 所以你在公园时是嗑嗨状态  - 天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Wait, so you were high in the park? - My goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.34,0:17:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我几乎没吸入 我只是想让别人觉得我有趣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. I barely even inhaled. I just wanted to seem like I was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.14,0:17:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前在一个派对 是哈密尔顿斯维尼家的人举办的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was at a party, hosted by the Hamilton-Sweeneys.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.81,0:17:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许你听过他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe you've heard of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.31,0:17:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么印象\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Doesn't ring a bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.23,0:17:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的室友威廉 他的父亲是派对主人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My roommate, William, his father was the host,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.65,0:17:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过他不在场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}though he wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.57,0:17:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威廉也不在 他和他们疏远了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Neither was William. He's estranged from them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.03,0:18:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有高档外套可以穿去那样的派对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't have a suit nice enough to wear to a party like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.62,0:18:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邀请函要求夏季白色服装\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Summer whites, the invitation said.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.66,0:18:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我...借了威廉的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So I-- I borrowed William's.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.08,0:18:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以是他的外套 他的海洛因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So his jacket, his heroin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.09,0:18:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道他有这个习惯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Were you aware of his habit?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.30,0:18:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说过已经戒掉了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He told me it was in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.72,0:18:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很愚蠢地相信了他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Foolishly, I believed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.22,0:18:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瘾君子有这种本领 他们撒起谎来不打草稿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Addicts have that way about them. They lie as easy as they breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.47,0:18:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我没有撒谎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I am not a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.94,0:18:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过了 我在等巴士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is like I told you, I was waiting for the bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.94,0:18:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在等别的什么车或什么人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She was waiting for something or someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.61,0:18:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来时 她不见了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When I got back, she was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.49,0:18:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我循着声音走进公园\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When I followed that sound into the park,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.16,0:18:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...发现了她 我就向你们报警了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I-- I found her, and I called you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.00,0:18:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.67,0:19:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们就假设 你是个在错的时间出现的热心群众\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's say you're just a Good Samaritan with lousy timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.39,0:19:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不意味着你就洗脱嫌疑了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It doesn't mean you're off the hook just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.93,0:19:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经鉴定了你的弹药残留物 我们还要采集你的指纹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've been dusted for gunpowder residue and obliged us a set of fingerprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.73,0:19:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也得留下电话号码和地址\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm also gonna need your phone number and your address.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.86,0:19:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说谎 我会核实的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do not lie. I will be checking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.99,0:19:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能离开城市 在结案前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you don't leave the city. Till this case is solved,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.99,0:19:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你将一直是谋杀未遂案的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you will continue to be a person of interest
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.03,0:19:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫌疑人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in an attempted murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.28,0:19:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 帕尔撒警探\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Detective Parsa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.96,0:19:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你们找到真凶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I hope you find who did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.05,0:19:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只和她简短地聊了聊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I only spoke to her briefly,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.38,0:19:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是感觉她是个生活丰富多彩的女孩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but she seemed like a girl with so much to live for.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.98,0:19:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子 起床了 早上好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Son, wake up. Well, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.57,0:19:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老天爷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.15,0:20:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我不该在这里 我不属于这里 抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sorry. I shouldn't be here. I don't belong here. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.41,0:20:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是上帝的地方 任何人都属于这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is God's house. Everyone belongs here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.00,0:20:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们甚至不会锁门\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We don't even lock the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.12,0:20:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是犹太教的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I'm Jewish.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.58,0:20:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是被领养的 但...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm adopted, but--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.33,0:20:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我父母和我说了这事后 我嘴里冒出来的第一句话是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, the first thing I said when my parents told me was,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.63,0:20:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“我不是被选择的 ” 他们说:“你是 查理 我们选择了你”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"So, I'm not chosen?" And they said, "You are, Charlie, by us."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.55,0:20:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.51,0:20:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这话无意冒犯长岛花山的威斯巴格一家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}no offense to the Weisbargers of Flower Hill, Long Island,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.39,0:20:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是从圣经的角度而言 这不是同一个概念\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but, like, biblically speaking, that's not really the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.43,0:20:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子 你为什么来这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's brought you here, son?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.19,0:20:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了一件可怕的事 而我不知道该怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Something terrible happened, and I don't really know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.86,0:20:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道她是否平安无事 但一部分的我不想知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wanna know if she's okay, but part of me wants to not know
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.41,0:20:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只想保持不知道的状态 因为如果她出事了 那我...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and wants to keep not knowing, because if she's not, then I--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.46,0:20:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道自己会做出什么事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't really know what I'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.63,0:20:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Like, if she--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.84,0:21:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她没能存活 那我也无法活下去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If she does not survive, then I will not survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.26,0:21:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...明白吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Does that-- Does that make any sense?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.81,0:21:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很抱歉 太难解释了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry. It's too much to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.11,0:21:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯特 你能把声音调小吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cate, can you turn that down?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.95,0:21:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太大声了 我犯头痛了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's really loud. It's giving me a headache.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.62,0:21:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可能是因为你宿醉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or you're really hungover.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.08,0:21:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道那是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How do you even know what that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.88,0:21:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你承认啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, you admit it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.80,0:21:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都没承认\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I admit nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.47,0:21:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉让你久等 蕾根\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sorry for the wait, Regan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.84,0:21:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父亲在睡觉 我不想打扰他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your father is sleeping, and I really don't want to disturb him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.39,0:21:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们还要赶航班 - 好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We've got the flight ahead of us. - Okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.39,0:21:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那正是我打给你的原因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but that's why I'm calling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.89,0:21:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莫里或菲莉希亚和他聊过吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did Amory or Felicia speak with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.81,0:22:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他在落地前需要知道一些事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because there are some things he needs to know before he lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.15,0:22:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们没有 医生也警告过 不要有不必要的压力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They haven't. And the doctors warned against unnecessary stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.44,0:22:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 但只可惜 这次的压力是必要的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, but unfortunately, this stress is necessary,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.16,0:22:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他能消化这消息的时间越多 就越好 你能不能叫醒他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and the more time he has to process it, the better. So, if you could just wake him
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.78,0:22:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他听电话 我会很感激\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and put him on the phone, I'd really appreciate that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.25,0:22:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 蕾根 我不会这么做 你可以在他回家后和他聊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry, Regan. I'm not gonna do that. You can talk to him when he's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.75,0:22:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他挂我电话 这混蛋挂我电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He hung up on me. The fucker hung up on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.34,0:22:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别盯着我看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Redirect those eyeballs somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.43,0:22:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为你在和我说话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought you were talking to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.35,0:22:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你还和谁在聊  - 等等 威尔 等一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Who else were you talking to? - Hold on, Will. Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.81,0:22:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 是的 抱歉 我不能...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey. Yes. Sorry, I-- I couldn't--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.03,0:22:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我昨晚没去派对 我有些事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't make it to the party last night. Something came up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.57,0:22:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要解释 你是个懦夫 我懂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No need for an explanation. You're a coward, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.24,0:22:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真希望我能打给世界上其他任何一个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I wish I had literally anyone else in the world to call.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.07,0:22:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我父亲今天从妙佑诊所回来时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But when my father gets back from the Mayo Clinic today,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.58,0:22:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他会被直接带到法官室接受审问\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he's going to be taken directly to the judge's chamber to be arraigned.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.33,0:22:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.87,0:23:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 指控是什么  - 电信诈骗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What's the charge? - Wire fraud.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.25,0:23:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么...那...是联邦罪行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What-- That's a-- That's a federal offense.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.30,0:23:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 显然他可能被判20年监禁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. Apparently, it can get you 20 years in prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.59,0:23:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且第五大道房产的贷款也要到期了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not to mention we have loans coming due on the 5th Avenue buildings.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.76,0:23:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 如果银行不愿与我们做生意 那我们会失去一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, if the banks won't do business with us, well, we could lose everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.10,0:23:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾根 你的父亲绝不会 做任何不诚信的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Regan, your father would never do anything dishonest.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.81,0:23:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显然 不是故意做 像...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, obviously-- Not on purpose, like--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.44,0:23:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我有多兢兢业业 但如果...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know how diligent I've been, but if--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.19,0:23:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法看完他签过名的每一份文件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't look at every document that has his signature on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.94,0:23:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我甚至不知道他是否知道任何情况\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not even sure if he knows anything about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.40,0:23:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可能完全不知情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or if he's gonna be totally blindsided.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.28,0:23:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莫里怎么想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What does Amory think?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.33,0:23:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我知道就好了 我联系不上他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wish I knew. I can't get a hold of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.37,0:23:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一位律师给我留言说 一切都处理好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got a message through a lawyer that said everything had been taken care of
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.42,0:23:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该留在家里 但我...不能这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I should just stay home, and I-- I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.67,0:23:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以...总之 我知道今天不是轮到你 但如果你可以...让孩子...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So-- Anyway, I know it's not your day, but if you could-- The kids could just--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.93,0:23:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊 当然我会照顾他们 这是我至少该做的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, my God. Yeah, of course I'll take 'em. It's the least I could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.97,0:23:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 可不是嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, yeah. No shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.43,0:23:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过得说 今天我状态不太好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gotta say, they're not exactly getting me at my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.27,0:24:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会比我更糟糕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can't be worse than I am right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.15,0:24:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我记忆里 你喝醉后都是优雅的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've never known you to be anything other than an elegant drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.70,0:24:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽快过来 好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just get here as soon as you can, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.41,0:24:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.66,0:24:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.87,0:24:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 帕尔撒 - 麦克法登\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Parsa. - McFadden.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.42,0:24:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警探 有什么消息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Detective, what's the latest?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.04,0:24:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该了解我的一点是 我最讨厌医院\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One thing you should know about me, I fucking hate hospitals.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.63,0:24:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是...谁会喜欢 那女孩情况如何\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, yeah. Who doesn't? How's the girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.96,0:24:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.13,0:24:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 父亲呢  - 崩溃了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- And the father? - A wreck.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.76,0:24:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨曼莎是他的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Samantha's his whole life.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.47,0:24:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老婆在小萨11岁时离开 和一个瑜伽老师搬到加州\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wife left when Sam was 11, moved to California with a yoga instructor.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.81,0:24:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从此杳无音讯 够冷酷的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Never heard from her again. Brutal.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.64,0:24:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于她在公园做什么 他有没有任何想法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did he have any thoughts on what she was doing in the park?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.85,0:24:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 萨曼莎是个好学生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. Samantha was a good student.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.56,0:24:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿奖学金进了纽约大学 但她在城里有精彩的生活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Got into NYU on scholarship, but she's got a big life in the city,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.44,0:24:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的父亲有自己的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and her father has his own problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.90,0:24:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说他制作烟花 但生意不好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Apparently, he makes fireworks, but business isn't so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.32,0:24:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烟花啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fireworks, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.41,0:24:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小萨是摄影师 作家 喜欢城中心俱乐部的新音乐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sam's a photographer, a writer, into new music in downtown clubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.58,0:25:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要在第八大道和大学广场街的路口下车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm getting dropped at 8th and University Place.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.62,0:25:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 来找我吧 - 为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Come meet me. - Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.63,0:25:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里是她的宿舍 她有室友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's her dorm. Has a roommate.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.13,0:25:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 好的 那里见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, okay. I'll see you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.40,0:25:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊 怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jesus. What the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.19,0:25:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.78,0:25:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是血吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.91,0:25:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 是的 这是血 - 你还好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yes. This is blood. - You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.12,0:25:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是我的血 如果你是问这个的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not my blood if that's what you're asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.49,0:25:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果你只是普通问候 那么 不 我不好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But if you're just wondering in a more general sense, no, I'm not okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.33,0:25:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊 墨瑟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jesus, Merce.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.54,0:25:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样 昨晚我去了 汉密尔顿斯维尼的国庆日嘉年华派对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}See, last night, I went to the Hamilton-Sweeney Fourth of July gala.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.80,0:25:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父亲没去 但我见到了恶魔弟弟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}See, your father couldn't make it, but I did meet the demon uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.97,0:25:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很理解为什么给他起这个绰号\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Totally get the nickname.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.38,0:26:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但昨晚真正有趣的部分是之后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But the really interesting part of the night was later,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.89,0:26:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在公园发现一个女孩 她的头部中枪了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when I had found a girl in the park who had been shot in the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.69,0:26:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我作为她的谋杀未遂案嫌疑人被警察拘留\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was then taken into custody as a suspect in her attempted murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.98,0:26:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等...你认真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stop... You're serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.82,0:26:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察怎么可能觉得你枪击某人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How could the cops possibly think that you shot someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.41,0:26:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,90%是种族歧视\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd say 90% racism
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.83,0:26:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10%是他们发现的半克海洛因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and 10% the half-gram of heroin that they found
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.50,0:26:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 在你美丽的西服外套口袋里 - 好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- in the pocket of your lovely suit jacket... - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.17,0:26:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们扣留了 因为那成了证据\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...which they kept because it is now evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.59,0:26:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着 关于你昨晚的经历 我很抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, I am really sorry about your night
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.34,0:26:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也不是我把我的毒品放在你的外套里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but it's not like I kept my drugs in your jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.73,0:26:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我好几年没穿过那件该死的西服了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Plus, I haven't worn that fucking suit in years.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.19,0:26:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你上周才穿去米涅塔酒馆吃晚餐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You wore it for dinner at Minetta Tavern last week!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.03,0:26:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威廉 你说你会戒掉海洛因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}William, you told me you would quit using heroin!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.61,0:26:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我搬来和你同居的条件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was a condition of my moving in with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.07,0:27:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 “成瘾”不是平白无故叫的 对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. Well, they don't call it addiction for nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.71,0:27:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着 要不是你背着我去那个派对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, look. If you would have just not gone to that party behind my back,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.92,0:27:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这一切都不会发生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}then none of this would've happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.34,0:27:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你要另开一个话题争吵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, you're going to start a different fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.34,0:27:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不用继续这个话题了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so we don't have to finish this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.80,0:27:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是在被逼入绝境后推卸责任\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You always turn tables when you're cornered!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.76,0:27:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜欢被逼入绝境\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't like being cornered.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.43,0:27:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你和我一起去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wanted you to come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.72,0:27:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 墨瑟 听我说 好吗 我不想去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. Mercer, listen to me, okay? I didn't want to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.85,0:27:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的家人 那是我的邀请函\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's my family. That's my invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.11,0:27:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的西服 我该死的海洛因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My suit, my fucking heroin.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.23,0:27:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if-- if--
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.95,0:27:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你可以不要一天到晚关注我...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if you could just stop being so interested in me all the time--
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.49,0:27:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去哪 我在做什么 我来自哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where I go, what I'm doing, where I come from,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.12,0:27:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我朝血管里注射什么... 我们本可拥有美好生活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}what I fucking inject into my veins-- We could have a beautiful life.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.25,0:27:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是...为什么我什么都没和你说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is-- This is exactly why I didn't fucking say anything to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.83,0:27:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为...我知道你有多么爱批判人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because-- because I know how judgmental you can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.00,0:27:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我不...我不是在批判你 - 不是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'm not-- No, I'm not judging you. - No?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.38,0:27:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 威廉 我开始担心... - 好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- William, I am growing concerned... - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.76,0:28:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的健康 这会影响我们的关系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...for your health, for our relationship!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.55,0:28:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的关系 好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our relationship. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.18,0:28:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我问你个问题 你为什么对这事大惊小怪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let me ask you a question. How can you make such a big deal
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.35,0:28:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你此前都不知道这事的存在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}out of something that you didn't even know was happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.23,0:28:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.94,0:28:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这逻辑太扭曲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That is some twisted logic.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.86,0:28:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死 你真的是个艺术家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Damn, you-- you really are an artist.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.41,0:28:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 也许如果你更有创造力 你就会理解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, well, maybe if you were more creative, you would understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.78,0:28:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗 我此刻感到一股创造力在迸发\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know what? I am feeling a burst of creativity coming out of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.62,0:28:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的要半途离开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you seriously walking out?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.37,0:28:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 是的 真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, yeah, I seriously am.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.13,0:28:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...就站在那里 当真\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're-- You're just going to stand there? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.09,0:28:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 你觉得我挪不动你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What, you don't think that I can move you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.59,0:28:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你来试啊... - 真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You can try... - Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.97,0:28:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我希望你不会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...but I'm hoping that you won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.93,0:28:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 像木板一样坚硬 像石头一样强大...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay. Stiff as a board, strong as a rock. Stiff as a board, strong as--
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.33,0:29:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.71,0:29:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是太累了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm just so tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.59,0:29:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.10,0:29:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是一种病\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a sickness.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.23,0:29:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.82,0:29:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.66,0:29:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请别放弃我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please don't give up on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.48,0:30:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈咪...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mommy, Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.02,0:30:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯特 宝贝 怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cate, honey, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.53,0:30:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们昨晚见到的蓝色小鸟死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The blue bird we saw last night, it's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.78,0:30:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 别碰它 身上都是细菌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay. Don't touch it. It's full of germs.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.53,0:30:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概没有 它还没发出臭气或引来苍蝇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Doubtful. It's barely starting to smell or draw flies,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.74,0:30:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以死亡时间不长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so it hasn't been dead that long.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.62,0:30:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 鸟类犯罪现场调查专家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, avian crime scene investigator.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.96,0:30:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你确定它是死了 而不是在睡觉吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you sure it's dead and not just sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.42,0:30:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常确定 它中枪了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Quite sure. It's been shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.26,0:30:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中枪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.47,0:30:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看这里 肚子上有干净 穿透的伤口\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look here. A clean through-and-through wound to its belly.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.64,0:30:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会朝美丽的小鸟开枪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who would shoot a beautiful bird?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.19,0:31:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...不知道 宝贝 但我们最好处理掉它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I-- I don't know, honey, but we should probably get rid of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.86,0:31:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威尔 你能不能找个盒子什么的  我们把它放进去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Will, can you get, like, a box or something that we can put it in?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.57,0:31:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈 这只是一只愚蠢的死鸟 不需要给它举办葬礼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's just a dumb, dead bird, Mom. It doesn't need a funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.28,0:31:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要 我要找一朵花\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, it does. I'm going to find a flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.17,0:31:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 任何东西 报纸...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please? Anything, a newspaper--
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.29,0:31:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我不用碰它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just so I don't have to touch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.47,0:31:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布鲁克林为什么会有鹦鹉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is a parrot doing in Brooklyn?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.18,0:31:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是鹦鹉 是蓝蕉鹃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not a parrot. It's a great blue turaco.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.93,0:31:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是从布朗克斯动物园的 鸟类世界逃出来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Probably escaped from the World of Birds at the Bronx Zoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.94,0:31:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你多大  - 十岁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- How old are you? - Ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.48,0:31:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威尔12岁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Will's 12.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.20,0:31:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他以前和你一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He used to be like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.99,0:31:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对世界充满兴趣 你懂吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Interested in things, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.54,0:31:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.37,0:31:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 那是他吗 威尔  - 对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- That him? Will? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.67,0:32:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 威尔 你知道 金星是唯一顺时针自转的行星吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, Will. Did you know Venus is the only planet that spins clockwise?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.92,0:32:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.51,0:32:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 我好想你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey. I've missed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.72,0:32:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么 花\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's this? A flower?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.81,0:32:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(少女受害者头部中枪)
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.10,0:32:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 给我的吗  - 对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Is that for me? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.02,0:32:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 嗨 - 嗨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hey. - Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.90,0:32:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 不说“谢谢”呀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What, no "thank you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.78,0:32:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...开玩笑的 天啊 别生气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm-- I'm kidding, I'm kidding. Jesus. Come-- Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.45,0:32:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 威尔在那边 - 嘿 伙计\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Will's over there. - Hey, champ.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.75,0:32:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.37,0:32:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不一直这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is it ever?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.67,0:32:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 你爸今天到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey. Your dad's getting in today,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.13,0:32:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 所以他昨晚不在  - 对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- so he wasn't there last night? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.26,0:32:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 所以你没和他聊  - 还没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- So, you didn't talk to him? - Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.43,0:33:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 各位 我们做什么呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, guys. What are we gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.45,0:33:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.04,0:33:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查尔斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Charles,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.33,0:33:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你在哪  - 我在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- where are you? - I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.01,0:33:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小萨 醒醒 小萨 拜托\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sam, wake up. Sam, come on, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.18,0:33:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 嘿 - 嗨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hey. - Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.44,0:33:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 我以为你午饭后才来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hi. I wasn't expecting you till after lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.32,0:33:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把牛奶给我 谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pass me the milk, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.44,0:33:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 没问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.03,0:33:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在米奇那里一切可好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everything okay at Mickey's?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.20,0:33:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是...很好 我只是...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, yeah, fine. I just--
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.16,0:34:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是早起然后感到无聊 所以我...就回家了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just woke up early and got bored, so I-- I came home.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.62,0:34:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.25,0:34:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能拿走这个吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can I take this?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.84,0:34:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(中央公园枪击案影响了国庆烟花表演)
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.93,0:34:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(没有线索)
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.39,0:34:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(枪击案后48小时 成为悬案)
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.69,0:34:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(新年前夕在等待 爱你的小萨)
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.74,0:35:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(纽约大学 兰兹曼宿舍)
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.83,0:35:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道我们确切的目的地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Know exactly where we're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.29,0:35:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要和这里的谁聊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who we need to talk to here?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.96,0:35:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我压根不知道怎么在大学宿舍找路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hell if I know how a college dorm works.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.42,0:35:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当时住在家里 在莫霍克谷社区学院拿了45个学分就滚了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I lived at home, got my 45 credits from Mohawk Valley and split.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.55,0:35:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们找到负责人 然后找她的房间吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Guess we find someone in charge and find her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.26,0:35:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.18,0:35:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.94,0:35:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(在此给莱拉和小萨留言)
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.36,0:36:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(嗨 莱拉 下午2点 去公园的植物园找我们)
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.58,0:36:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 出了什么事  - 谁说出事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What happened? - Who said something happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.42,0:36:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们能进来问你几个问题吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}May we come in and ask you some questions, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.75,0:36:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.13,0:36:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最后一次见到萨曼莎是什么时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When was the last time you saw Samantha?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.59,0:36:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两周前吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Two weeks, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.93,0:36:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们俩都决定暑假留在宿舍 但她来来去去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We both decided to stay for the summer, but she comes and goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.02,0:36:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在图书馆当实习生 所以我工作日不在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've got an internship at the library, so I'm gone weekdays.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.48,0:36:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她大多夜晚和周末都不在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's gone most nights and weekends.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.32,0:36:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 她去哪了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah? Where does she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.32,0:36:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从没被邀请过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not that I've ever been invited,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.62,0:36:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她去看很多音乐会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but she goes to a lot of music shows.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.54,0:36:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的朋友是乐队的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Her friends are in some band.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.12,0:36:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是否记得乐队名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you remember the name of the band?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.00,0:36:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从没听说过他们 但名字是拉丁文\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've never heard of them, but it's Latin.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.92,0:37:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,类似“活在当下” 但不是这句\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's-- It's like carpe diem, but not.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.76,0:37:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在这里没什么个人物品\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She doesn't have much here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.35,0:37:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一开始有比较多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She started with more
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.43,0:37:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但越来越少 现在她基本不在这里过夜了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but it just got less and less, and now she barely sleeps here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.73,0:37:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得她在哪里过夜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, where do you think she's sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.73,0:37:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是否曾提到任何特别的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, she ever mention anybody special?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.28,0:37:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 但是她不怎么和我说自己的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, but she doesn't tell me a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.49,0:37:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小萨做了什么吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did Sam do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.00,0:37:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(纽约大学)\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You think there's anything to this music angle?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.83,0:37:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得这个音乐爱好方面是否会有线索
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.42,0:37:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说 我们只有这唯一的切入口 所以 会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, it's the only angle we have. So, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.01,0:37:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊猫女孩问小萨是否犯了什么事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Panda Girl asked if Sam was guilty of something,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.51,0:37:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而不是问她是不是受害者 这反映了她的个人喜好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}not if she was a victim. That says something about what she was into.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.01,0:37:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可能反映了熊猫女孩的内心 要我说 她挺爱评判人的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or it says something about Panda Girl. Kind of judgy, if you ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.77,0:37:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.78,0:38:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是...我在路上了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, yeah. On my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.15,0:38:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有老婆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You got a wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.20,0:38:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还有 你呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For now. What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.95,0:38:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢 怎么 我有没有老婆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What about me? What, do I have a wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.00,0:38:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 不 电话上的不是我老婆 那是犯罪现场组\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, no, that wasn't my wife. That was CSU.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.71,0:38:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们在犯罪现场准备好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're ready at the crime scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.01,0:38:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉希亚 不如你先去车上 我马上就过去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Felicia, why don't you go to the car? I'll be just a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.76,0:38:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比尔很快就落地 我们不能迟到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bill lands shortly. We can't be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.93,0:38:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我保证你的脸将会是他最先看到的脸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I promise yours will be the first face he sees.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.90,0:38:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚公园的事真是见不得光 很悲惨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sordid business in the park last night. Tragic.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.23,0:38:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说是个年轻女孩 什么样的禽兽...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Apparently, she was a young girl. What kind of animal--
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.40,0:38:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我很好奇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}By the way, I was curious,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.28,0:38:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉斯兰普莱特有去派对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}did Keith Lamplighter ever show up at the party?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.62,0:38:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不记得见过他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, I don't remember seeing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.67,0:38:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我查查\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let me check.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.00,0:39:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 他似乎没到场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, looks like he didn't show.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.21,0:39:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道他因为什么事无法到场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wonder what would have kept him away.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.26,0:39:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许他有更好的活动 祝你愉快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I guess he got a better offer. Have a good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.08,0:39:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Daddy! Daddy! Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.42,0:39:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(联邦调查局)
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.97,0:39:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 嗨 - 蕾根 宝贝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hi! - Regan, honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.09,0:39:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着 我不知道...别人对你说了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Listen, I don't know what-- what people have told you,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.14,0:39:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们必须和这些人一起走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but we're going to have to go with these men.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.97,0:39:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他必须独自走 你可以跟在后面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's coming alone. You can follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.72,0:39:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 等等 你们要给他铐手铐  - 怎么回事 我不...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Wait, are you fucking cuffing him? - What's happening? I don't--
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.94,0:39:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 你们觉得他会逃跑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What, do you think he's gonna flee?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.60,0:40:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是什么情况 我是清白的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whatever this is, I'm innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.65,0:40:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 我知道 你当然是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, I know. Of course you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.36,0:40:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们...我们...必须想办法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and they're-- And we're-- we're gonna have to figure this out,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.82,0:40:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这需要一些程序\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but it's gonna be a process.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.36,0:40:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我是在问 这是个...问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, I mean, I'm asking. It's a-- It's a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.20,0:40:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能和他一起去吗 拜托  我可以解释一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can I go with him, please? So that I can explain everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.25,0:40:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以解释\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.84,0:40:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们到那边见 亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll see you there, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.25,0:40:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们能对他轻一点吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you be careful with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.60,0:40:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道他们要给他铐手铐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You knew they were gonna cuff him.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.31,0:40:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不得不做出一些妥协\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We had to make some compromises.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.31,0:40:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们同意进行私下审问\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They agreed to this private arraignment
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.35,0:40:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就不用在周末把他拘留在“陵墓”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so they didn't have to hold him in the Tombs for the weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.77,0:40:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们给他戴手铐 给老人铐手铐 你真是失心疯了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They cuffed him. They handcuffed an old man. You're fucking insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.77,0:40:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着 我知道你很沮丧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, I know you're upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.46,0:41:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(警方戒严线 不得跨越)\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- How's it looking? - No one knows better than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.75,0:41:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 情况如何  - 没有新发现
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.42,0:41:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公园犯罪总是很难调查 人流量大 还有垃圾 枯叶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Park is always tough. Lots of traffic, trash and leaf litter.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.63,0:41:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边有发现\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Think we got something!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.19,0:41:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是个很棒的发现 可惜是对其他人的案子来说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's a great find, for somebody else's case.
